import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

function Navbar() {
  return (
    <header className="fixed top-0 w-full bg-transparent px-6 py-6 z-50">
      <nav className="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex justify-center space-x-10 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">
        <Link
          to="/"
          className="text-black hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Home
        </Link>
        <Link
          to="/about"
          className="text-black hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          About
        </Link>
        <Link
          to="/portfolio"
          className="text-black hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Portfolio
        </Link>
        <Link
          to="/contact"
          className="text-black hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Contact
        </Link>
      </nav>
    </header>
  );
}

export default Navbar;
